[[VDSM-Hooks/directlun]]            - Attach a LUN to a VM

[[VDSM-Hooks/faqemu]]               - Fake QEMU emulation (the VM will "think" it has VT extensions enabled)

[[VDSM-Hooks/fileinject]]           - Insert a file into the VM

[[VDSM-Hooks/floppy]]               - Attach a floppy image to the VM

[[VDSM-Hooks/hostusb]]              - Attach a hosts' USB device to the VM

[[VDSM-Hooks/hugepages]]            - Enable hugepages for the VM

[[VDSM-Hooks/isolatedprivatevlan]]  - Connect VM to an isolated private VLAN instead of a shared network

[[VDSM-Hooks/numa|numa]] - Pin a VM to a NUMA node(s)

[[VDSM-Hooks/pincpu]]               - Pin a VM to a set of CPU cores

[[VDSM-Hooks/promisc]]              - Start VM on a promiscous mode enabled network

[[VDSM-Hooks/qemucmdline]]          - Run an arbitrary QEMU command line

[[VDSM-Hooks/qos]]                  - Set a specific network QoS for a VM

[[VDSM-Hooks/scratchpad]]           - Start the VM with a disposable disk image, that will be removed when the VM is stopped

[[VDSM-Hooks/smartcard]]            - Enable SPICE  smartcard support for a VM

[[VDSM-Hooks/smbios]]               - Alter a VMs smbios domain entry

[[VDSM-Hooks/sriov]]                - Attach an SRIOV device to a VM

[[VDSM-Hooks/vhostmd]]              - Enable vhostmd for a VM

[[VDSM-Hooks/vmdisk]]               - Add an additional VM disk image

[[VDSM-Hooks/vmfex]]                - Attach a Cisco VM-FEX device to a VM
